<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Harry Potter Fan Club</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
      body {
        background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #d63e26, #ff5a3d);
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
      }

          .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 100px;
          }

          h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
          }

          p {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
          }

          table {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-collapse: collapse;
          }

          th, td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ffffff;
          }

          th {
            background-color: #d63e26;
            font-weight: bold;
          }

          tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #ff5a3d;
          }

          .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #d63e26;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
          }

          .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #ff5a3d;
          }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Desafio de deploy con Fake en RoR!</h1>
      <p>La siguiente informaci√≥n ha sido generada con la gema Fake:</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Location</th>
            <th>House</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% @characteres.each do |char| %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= char.name %></td>
            <td><%= char.location %></td>
            <td><%= char.house %></td>
          </tr>
          <% end %>

        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
